original: The High Performance Computing Array (HPCA) is a multiblock structure used for creating Compute Work Units (CWU/t) for more complex Assembly Line Research Data. The structure has a flexible 3x3 area which can be filled in any way with HPCA components. Different components can provide different amounts of Computation, Cooling, as well as Energy Cost, Coolant Cost, and Heat Production. When used with a Bridge Component, the HPCA can connect to Network Switches for combining and routing Computation from multiple sources to one or more destinations.
translation: 高性能计算阵列（HPCA）是个多方块结构，用于为更复杂的装配线研究数据提供计算工作单元（CWU/t）。该结构中有3×3的区域可以以任意方式填充HPCA组件，不同的组件提供不同数量的算力，冷却与能源成本，并且影响热量的产出与冷却液的消耗。当存在桥接组件时，HPCA可以连接入网络交换机，让不同来源的算力整合并输出到一个或多个目的地。

translation: 返回指定区间（含边界）内的随机数。

original: {random <min> <max>} -> a random number between min and max (inclusive)
translation: {random <最小值> <最大值>} -> 介于最小值和最大值之间的随机数（含边界）

original: Returns the redstone signal strength or sets the redstone output strength
translation: 返回或设置红石信号强度

original: {redstone get <up|down|north|south|east|west>} -> redstone signal strength (0-15) at the specified side
translation: {redstone get <up|down|north|south|east|west>} -> 指定面的红石信号强度（0-15）

original: {redstone get link <slot_index> <freq_slot_index>} -> redstone signal strength of a Create redstone link frequency specified by a linked controller in slot #slot_index. freq_slot_index is the index of the frequency inside the controller (from left to right, 0-6)
translation: {redstone get link <槽位索引> <频率槽位索引>} -> 指定的中央监视器槽位（槽位索引）中无线红石遥控器链接的机械动力红石频率上的信号强度。频率槽位索引是无线红石遥控器内部频率的索引（从左到右，0–6）

original: {redstone set <power>} -> empty string, sets the redstone output strength from this cover's side
translation: {redstone set <强度>} -> 空字符串，设置红石信号输出强度，从此覆盖板方向输出

original: {redstone set link <slot_index> <freq_slot_index> <power>} -> empty string, broadcasts the specified redstone power on the specified Create redstone link frequency
translation: {redstone set link <槽位索引> <频率槽位索引> <信号强度>} -> 空字符串，在指定的无线红石遥控器链接的机械动力红石频率上，设为指定的红石信号强度

original: Returns the text from the second arguments, repeated the amount of times specified in the first argument.
translation: 返回重复若干次（第一个参数）的文本（第二个参数）。

original: {repeat <amount> <text>} -> text repeated the specified amount of times
translation: {repeat <数量> <文本>} -> 重复指定次数的文本

original: Returns the argument at the specified index (starting from 0)
translation: 返回指定索引处的参数（从0开始）
{select <索引编号> [参数1] [参数2] [参数3] ... -> 指定索引处的参数

original: Returns the text from the first text, displaying it as if it was crossed out
translation: 返回有删除线的文本（第一个参数），就像被划掉一样

original: Returns arguments from with indexes from l (inclusive) to r (exclusive) (starting from 0)
translation: 返回参数列表中索引范围为左（含边界）至右（不含）的元素（从0开始计）

original: {subList <left> <right> [arg0] [arg1] ...} -> all arguments with indexes from l to r separated by spaces
translation: {subList <左> <右> [参数0] [参数1] ...} -> 从<左>到<右>的所有参数，以空格分隔

original: Returns the amount of ticks passed from when this cover was placed.
translation: 返回从安装此覆盖板时起经过的tick。

original: Returns the ASCII code of the provided character
Returns the characters of the provided string with spaces between them
translation: 返回将提供的字符串按字符分隔并以空格连接的结果

original: Example: {toChars example} -> 'e x a m p l e'
translation: 例：{toChars example} -> 'e x a m p l e'

original: Returns the text from the first argument, underlined
translation: 返回有下划线的文本（第一个参数）

original: Returns the voltage in the wire/cable the cover is on.
translation: 返回覆盖板所贴附的的导线/线缆的电压大小。

original: Storing computer monitor cover configuration data
translation: 存储电脑屏幕覆盖板的配置数据

original: Binding to a transmitter cover at %s %s %s facing %s
translation: 绑定至无线发信器，位于%s %s %s，朝向%s
与末影连接覆盖板交互

original: Can interact with private channels if provided with a data item bound to a player
translation: 如果提供一个绑定了玩家的数据容器，就可以与私人频道交互
{ender item <频道> [数据容器(玩家)槽位]} -> 物品数量
{ender fluid <频道> [数据容器(玩家)槽位]} -> 流体量
{ender redstone <频道> [数据容器(玩家)槽位] -> 红石信号强度

original: {ender redstone <channel> <player_data_item_slot> <signal> -> sets the redstone signal outputed to the ender redstone link, returns empty string
translation: {ender redstone <频道> <数据容器(玩家)槽位> <红石信号强度> -> 设置输出到末影红石连接覆盖板的红石信号强度，返回空字符串

original: The player_data_item_slot argument may be left empty (not 0, empty string)
translation: 数据容器(玩家)槽位参数可以留空（不是0，空字符串）
